&lt;p&gt;· EPA Certification&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· NATE certified (required within 1 year of date of hire)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· OSHA 10 or OSHA 30&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· 5 years of HVAC Experience&lt;/p&gt;
