&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to advance your career with the #1 HVAC Company in Northern Nevada? We are looking for a Delivery Driver to join our growing team! The ideal candidate possesses a high level of reliability, precision, attention to detail, an exceptional driving record, and the ability to perform all duties in a busy work environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Delivery Driver reports to the Facilities Manager and is responsible for delivering parts to technicians in the field, picking up parts from suppliers, assisting in the parts warehouse and shop when needed, and all other duties as assigned.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daily Job Tasks:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Deliver parts to field employees, at the jobsite&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Pick up parts from suppliers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Assist with inventory as needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Assist in the warehouse as needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Help with cleanup around the shop and warehouse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Help with loading trucks in the morning&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· All other duties assigned by management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working Conditions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work will be performed in both indoor and outdoor settings, in various weather conditions. Lifting up to 70lbs is required. Must be able to work in hot and cold environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Will need to be able to work late hours and weekends, when necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· High school diploma or equivalent&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· One year delivery driver experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Valid Nevada driver’s license&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Clean driving record with no moving violations in the last 5 years&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Ability to represent SIERRA AIR INC. in a professional manner with customers, vendors, staff, and the general public&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Organized and detail oriented&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Ability to work under pressure&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Ability to pass drug test/background screening&lt;/p&gt;
